This paper discusses the annotation of medical literature, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper may also be relevant to the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI) due to the use of annotation and agreement analysis.
